이미지 인식 후 텍스트화¶

In [12]:
outfile = "out_text.txt"
In [13]:
f = open(outfile, "a", encoding='utf-8-sig')
for i in range(1, filelimit + 1):
    filename = "page_"+str(i)+".jpg"
    text = str(((pytesseract.image_to_string(Image.open(filename)))))
    text = text.replace('-\n', '')
    f.write(text)
f.close()
